  "content:encoded": "\n<p>Reuters <a href=\"https://app.assets.reuters.com/e/er?utm_campaign=Reuters%20Best%20Weekly_NWSLTR_NEW_GLOB_B2B_2201&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&utm_content=B2B%20220929%20NEWS%20GLOB%20REUTERS%20BEST%20AWARE%20NWSLTR%20WEEKLY&s=2124157686&lid=29434&elqTrackId=DAF9A57B3AB516D89F1C79268AB8088F&elq=030da3d281a14ea89203daf25e7b6331&elqaid=2382&elqat=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">exclusively reported </a>major developments in a process that saw the largest Latin American development bank, IDB, oust its president, Mauricio Claver-Carone, after an independent ethics probe found &#8220;direct evidence&#8221; that he had an intimate relationship with a subordinate and violated other bank rules.Â Reuters <a href=\"https://app.assets.reuters.com/e/er?utm_campaign=Reuters%20Best%20Weekly_NWSLTR_NEW_GLOB_B2B_2201&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&utm_content=B2B%20220929%20NEWS%20GLOB%20REUTERS%20BEST%20AWARE%20NWSLTR%20WEEKLY&s=2124157686&lid=29433&elqTrackId=4C3DA9D82E03BC45B9CB75F57085F497&elq=030da3d281a14ea89203daf25e7b6331&elqaid=2382&elqat=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">first</a> broke news of the investigation in April this year and also revealed the probe&#8217;s <a href=\"https://app.assets.reuters.com/e/er?utm_campaign=Reuters%20Best%20Weekly_NWSLTR_NEW_GLOB_B2B_2201&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&utm_content=B2B%20220929%20NEWS%20GLOB%20REUTERS%20BEST%20AWARE%20NWSLTR%20WEEKLY&s=2124157686&lid=29410&elqTrackId=C23A25B343F56452324AE4A7FBF41135&elq=030da3d281a14ea89203daf25e7b6331&elqaid=2382&elqat=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">findings </a>and the bank <a href=\"https://app.assets.reuters.com/e/er?utm_campaign=Reuters%20Best%20Weekly_NWSLTR_NEW_GLOB_B2B_2201&utm_medium=email&utm_source=Eloqua&utm_content=B2B%20220929%20NEWS%20GLOB%20REUTERS%20BEST%20AWARE%20NWSLTR%20WEEKLY&s=2124157686&lid=29412&elqTrackId=6C10521059C8912C10858D01B01B918A&elq=030da3d281a14ea89203daf25e7b6